{"tid":2274040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：無與中共討論美國大選 只關心如何把香港與中國完全合併","createTime":"2020-11-06T07:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T14:42:44.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"423908e722bd55721e05a65b591caffc13672861","tid":2274040,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:23:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭：無與韓正討論美國大選<br />\n<br />\n正在北京的行政長官林鄭月娥表示，與副總理韓正會面時無討論過美國大選，指關心香港融入國家發展大局的工作。她指美國與香港關係堅實而牢固，希望未來與美國政府仍保持堅實及相互尊重的關係。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥批評，過去一年美國官，持續干涉中國及香港內部事務，在國際關係中是完全不合理，強調每個政府都要尊重另一個地區及國家司法。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2365096&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9gDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=ad8db060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2365096</a>"},{"pid":"3bd3f30243a6441d33203dc7193a5c20f7b57653","tid":2274040,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"香港一早已淪陷"},{"pid":"bfffb24c8aa87c457d3578e2bdc58ad420b3b181","tid":2274040,"uid":59976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"美國不用擔心，拜登會處理一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef5cedba8add21b423efc787220ab2e2aa5f963","tid":2274040,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"62acd002ba919dff19b0a9881b38b5de76da8c90","tid":2274040,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"none of your business"},{"pid":"d6c1526a6c75d3656b642d8284f7b77b52f728ce","tid":2274040,"uid":377617,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"是旦啦 香港淪陷係遲早問題 這點市民唔擔心<br />\n係估唔到美國都俾中共入侵咁解姐"},{"pid":"aba82d884318f14b1f71ed37bffe6fe4e0b8fc08","tid":2274040,"uid":283080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit